典型的roles目录结构：
roles/
    xxx.yml
    common/
        files/
        templates/
        tasks/main.yml
        handlers/main.yml
        vars/main.yml
        meta/
    xxx/
        files/如脚本或者tar包等等
        templates/如配置文件等等模板文件
        tasks/main.yml
        handlers/main.yml
        vars/main.yml
        meta/一些依赖
 
 
 
在playbook中引用：
- name: ***
  hosts: xxx
  remote_user: root
  roles:
    - common
    - xxx
